---
title: gRPC streaming APIs (quiver-proto / server)
---
sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Client SDK
  participant S as quiver-server (tonic)
  participant E as Engine
  C->>S: client-stream Upsert(batch...)
  loop batches
    C->>S: UpsertChunk
    S->>E: buffered apply
  end
  S-->>C: UpsertSummary
  C->>S: Scroll(filter)
  loop pages
    E-->>S: page
    S-->>C: server-stream ScrollChunk
  end
